-- my-ds.page.body:

`doc-site` have inbuilt provision of adding `right-sidebar` for additional
components to be shown on right-side of `page` component. 

Add `sidebar: true` attribute to your `page` component.

-- note.note: NOTE

Click on download icon of below code-block. `right-sidebar.ftd` file will be
downloaded. Add this file inside your `fastn` project and deploy or run `fastn
serve` on your localhost. Access your localhost in browser
e.g.`http://127.0.0.1:8000/right-sidebar/` you will see right-sidebar inside
your page component.

-- ds.code: Example of `right-sidebar` inside `extra-headers` as child
lang: ftd
